Comparing the 7-day averages of daily confirmed cases from the past 7 days and those from 8-14 days ago, case counts have increased by 11.7%, while daily reported deaths have increased by 6.9%. Similar comparative 7-day averages in the USA show a 39.9% increase in daily reported cases and a 39.2% increase in reported deaths.

Impression: The global daily reported over 650 000 newly confirmed infections in the past 24 hours with over 267.40 million cumulative reported cases and over 5.28 million reported deaths. - Mod.UBA]
